# when "Require review from Code Owners" is enabled in branch protection,
# enforces that review before merge. Rules use last-match-wins: the most
# specific matching pattern below decides the reviewer for a given path.
#
# Syntax reference:
# https://docs.github.com/articles/about-code-owners

